A cyberpunk-style digital illustration of a glowing, translucent jar floating in a neon-lit void, its glass surface etched with intricate circuit patterns. Inside the jar, layers of luminous holographic blueprints and architectural schematics are suspended in mid-air, representing UI definitions stored within. Mechanical tendrils extend from the jar's opening, reaching outward but some snapping back as if blocked by an invisible barrier. The scene is bathed in electric blue and magenta light, with rain streaking down in the background against towering dark server monoliths. Small pixelated fragments orbit the jar like digital debris, some successfully entering while others bounce away, visualizing the selective nature of resource access.
